---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro'
import Hero from '../../components/Hero.astro'
---
<BaseLayout title="About Me">
  <Header />
  <Hero
    headline="About"
    lede="I'm a Product Designer and Frontend Engineer focused on creating amazing products and services."
  />

  <section class="section">
    <p class="section-label">A quick tour</p>
    <div class="split">
      <div class="panel">
        <ul class="link-list">
          <li><a href="/work/">My Work</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://pablonoel.com/resume/">My Resume</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://pablonoel.com/articles/">My Articles</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://pablonoel.com/analog/">My Passion</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="panel">
        <p>
          I've held a variety of design roles since the late 1990s. I studied Biotechnology,
          Engineering and Communications, but my love for design was always greater.
        </p>
        <p>
          I'm a passionate photographer who loves to understand and repair old cameras.
          I'm a devotee of medium format. With some friends we have a podcast where we
          talk about analog photography.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <p class="section-label">Selected photographs</p>
    <div class="gallery">
      <img src="/assets/about/about_001.jpg" alt="Analog photo 1" loading="lazy" />
      <img src="/assets/about/about_002.jpg" alt="Analog photo 2" loading="lazy" />
      <img src="/assets/about/about_003.jpg" alt="Analog photo 3" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <p class="section-label">My process</p>
    <div class="split">
      <div class="panel">
        <p>
          I believe we can't look to the future without understanding our present. Context
          shapes our ability to foresee what's next. Design should embrace science and art,
          stand on the shoulders of technology, and look into our history to create a story
          we can all relate to.
        </p>
        <blockquote>"Design is not added value; design is value." — Gui Bonsiepe</blockquote>
        <p>
          My background begins with the Ulm Model and grows every day through visionaries
          such as Bruno Latour, Tomas Maldonado, and Gui Bonsiepe.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="panel">
        <ol class="process">
          <li>Understand</li>
          <li>Plan</li>
          <li>Involve</li>
          <li>Research</li>
          <li>Instrumentalize</li>
          <li>Prototype</li>
          <li>Test</li>
          <li>Develop</li>
          <li>Deliver</li>
          <li>Refine</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section contact">
    <p class="section-label">Contact me</p>
    <p>
      I'm looking to work with amazing people and meaningful projects. If you think someone
      like me would be a good fit, let me know.
    </p>
    <p>
      +56 9 4946 0085<br />
      <a href="mailto:hello@pablonoel.com">hello@pablonoel.com</a><br />
      Santiago, Chile
    </p>
    <p class="note">
      All photos featured are mine, except where noted. Profile photos by
      <a href="http://fernandarequena.com">Fernanda Requena</a>.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
